I"b<h1 id="data-binding">Data Binding</h1>

<p>The section will help you answer the following questions:</p>

<ul>
  <li>How can I store data to retrieve at a later time?</li>
  <li>Much of the code I write in a Windows forms application is changing the state of the UI. How can I reduce the amount of UI code I write?</li>
  <li>What is Data Binding?</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="learning-objectives">Learning Objectives</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Read and write data to and from a file.</li>
  <li>Explain the role of data binding in a Windows Forms Application.</li>
  <li>Develop a Form class that uses data binding.</li>
</ul>
